panels.title: Total Stars (Current)

panels.description: Follows date range. Count of unique community contributors who created PRs in the rolling 7-day window ending on each date.

targets.queryText:
WITH weekly_contributors AS (
  SELECT 
    date(created_at) as pr_date,
    repo,
    author
  FROM pull_requests
  WHERE json_extract(data, '$.author_association') NOT IN ('OWNER', 'MEMBER', 'COLLABORATOR')
    AND repo IN ('agent-builder','agent-sop','docs','evals','mcp-server','private-docs-staging','private-sdk-python-staging','private-sdk-typescript-staging','private-tools-staging','samples','sdk-python','sdk-typescript','strands-action','strandsagents.com','tools','.github','private-samples-staging','private-strands-action-staging')
)
SELECT 
  CAST(strftime('%s', d.date) as INTEGER) as time,
  d.repo as metric,
  (
    SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT wc.author)
    FROM weekly_contributors wc
    WHERE wc.repo = d.repo
      AND wc.pr_date > date(d.date, '-7 days')
      AND wc.pr_date <= d.date
  ) as value
FROM daily_metrics d
WHERE d.repo IN ('agent-builder','agent-sop','docs','evals','mcp-server','private-docs-staging','private-sdk-python-staging','private-sdk-typescript-staging','private-tools-staging','samples','sdk-python','sdk-typescript','strands-action','strandsagents.com','tools','.github','private-samples-staging','private-strands-action-staging')
  AND CAST(strftime('%s', d.date) as INTEGER) >= $__from / 1000
  AND CAST(strftime('%s', d.date) as INTEGER) <= $__to / 1000
ORDER BY d.date ASC
targets.rawQueryText:

panels.title: Rejected PRs (Daily)

panels.description: Follows date range. Daily count of PRs that waited >48 hours for first review.

targets.queryText:
SELECT 
  CAST(strftime('%s', date(first_review_at)) as INTEGER) as time,
  repo as metric,
  COUNT(*) as value
FROM (
  SELECT 
    pr.repo,
    pr.number,
    pr.created_at,
    MIN(reviews.submitted_at) as first_review_at
  FROM pull_requests pr
  INNER JOIN pr_reviews reviews 
    ON pr.repo = reviews.repo AND pr.number = reviews.pr_number
  GROUP BY pr.repo, pr.number
  HAVING (julianday(MIN(reviews.submitted_at)) - julianday(pr.created_at)) * 24 > 48
) bottlenecks
WHERE repo IN ('agent-builder','agent-sop','docs','evals','mcp-server','private-docs-staging','private-sdk-python-staging','private-sdk-typescript-staging','private-tools-staging','samples','sdk-python','sdk-typescript','strands-action','strandsagents.com','tools','.github','private-samples-staging','private-strands-action-staging')
  AND CAST(strftime('%s', date(first_review_at)) as INTEGER) >= $__from / 1000
  AND CAST(strftime('%s', date(first_review_at)) as INTEGER) <= $__to / 1000
GROUP BY date(first_review_at), repo
ORDER BY first_review_at ASC
targets.rawQueryText:
SELECT 
  CAST(strftime('%s', date(first_review_at)) as INTEGER) as time,
  repo as metric,
  COUNT(*) as value
FROM (
  SELECT 
    pr.repo,
    pr.number,
    pr.created_at,
    MIN(reviews.submitted_at) as first_review_at
  FROM pull_requests pr
  INNER JOIN pr_reviews reviews 
    ON pr.repo = reviews.repo AND pr.number = reviews.pr_number
  GROUP BY pr.repo, pr.number
  HAVING (julianday(MIN(reviews.submitted_at)) - julianday(pr.created_at)) * 24 > 48
) bottlenecks
WHERE repo IN (${repo:singlequote})
  AND CAST(strftime('%s', date(first_review_at)) as INTEGER) >= $__from / 1000
  AND CAST(strftime('%s', date(first_review_at)) as INTEGER) <= $__to / 1000
GROUP BY date(first_review_at), repo
ORDER BY first_review_at ASC

panels.description: Follows date range. 7-day rolling average of lines changed per day. Days >10k lines filtered out.

targets.queryText:

panels.title: Code Churn (7-Day Rolling)

panels.description: Follows date range. 30-day rolling average of (PRs merged / PRs opened)  100%.

targets.queryText:
SELECT 
  CAST(strftime('%s', date) as INTEGER) as time,
  repo as metric,
  AVG(
    CAST(merged_count AS FLOAT) / NULLIF(total_count, 0) * 100
  ) OVER (PARTITION BY repo ORDER BY date ROWS BETWEEN 29 PRECEDING AND CURRENT ROW) as value
FROM (
  SELECT 
    date(COALESCE(merged_at, closed_at)) as date,
    repo,
    SUM(CASE WHEN merged_at IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as merged_count,
    COUNT(*) as total_count
  FROM pull_requests
  WHERE (merged_at IS NOT NULL OR (state = 'closed' AND merged_at IS NULL))
    AND repo IN ('agent-builder','agent-sop','docs','evals','mcp-server','private-docs-staging','private-sdk-python-staging','private-sdk-typescript-staging','private-tools-staging','samples','sdk-python','sdk-typescript','strands-action','strandsagents.com','tools','.github','private-samples-staging','private-strands-action-staging')
  GROUP BY date(COALESCE(merged_at, closed_at)), repo
) subquery
WHERE CAST(strftime('%s', date) as INTEGER) >= $__from / 1000
  AND CAST(strftime('%s', date) as INTEGER) <= $__to / 1000
ORDER BY date ASC
targets.rawQueryText:
SELECT 
  CAST(strftime('%s', date) as INTEGER) as time,
  repo as metric,
  AVG(
    CAST(merged_count AS FLOAT) / NULLIF(total_count, 0) * 100
  ) OVER (PARTITION BY repo ORDER BY date ROWS BETWEEN 29 PRECEDING AND CURRENT ROW) as value
FROM (
  SELECT 
    date(COALESCE(merged_at, closed_at)) as date,
    repo,
    SUM(CASE WHEN merged_at IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as merged_count,
    COUNT(*) as total_count
  FROM pull_requests
  WHERE (merged_at IS NOT NULL OR (state = 'closed' AND merged_at IS NULL))
    AND repo IN (${repo:singlequote})
  GROUP BY date(COALESCE(merged_at, closed_at)), repo
) subquery
WHERE CAST(strftime('%s', date) as INTEGER) >= $__from / 1000
  AND CAST(strftime('%s', date) as INTEGER) <= $__to / 1000
ORDER BY date ASC

targets.queryText:
-- Internal Time to First Review
SELECT 
  CAST(strftime('%s', date(first_response)) as INTEGER) as time,
  repo || ' (Internal)' as metric,
  AVG((julianday(first_response) - julianday(created_at)) * 24) 
    OVER (PARTITION BY repo ORDER BY date(first_response) ROWS BETWEEN 13 PRECEDING AND CURRENT ROW) as value
FROM (
  SELECT 
    pr.repo,
    pr.number,
    pr.created_at,
    MIN(CASE 
      WHEN reviews.submitted_at IS NOT NULL THEN reviews.submitted_at
      WHEN comments.created_at IS NOT NULL THEN comments.created_at
    END) as first_response
  FROM pull_requests pr
  LEFT JOIN pr_reviews reviews ON pr.repo = reviews.repo AND pr.number = reviews.pr_number
  LEFT JOIN pr_review_comments comments ON pr.repo = comments.repo AND pr.number = comments.pr_number
  WHERE json_extract(pr.data, '$.author_association') IN ('OWNER', 'MEMBER', 'COLLABORATOR')
  GROUP BY pr.repo, pr.number
  HAVING first_response IS NOT NULL
) responses
WHERE repo IN ('agent-builder','agent-sop','docs','evals','mcp-server','private-docs-staging','private-sdk-python-staging','private-sdk-typescript-staging','private-tools-staging','samples','sdk-python','sdk-typescript','strands-action','strandsagents.com','tools','.github','private-samples-staging','private-strands-action-staging')

panels.title: Time to First Review (14-Day Rolling)

panels.description: Follows date range. Daily count of first-time vs returning contributors.

targets.queryText:
WITH first_contributions AS (
  SELECT 
    author,
    MIN(date(created_at)) as first_pr_date
  FROM pull_requests
  WHERE json_extract(data, '$.author_association') NOT IN ('OWNER', 'MEMBER', 'COLLABORATOR')
    AND author NOT LIKE '%[bot]%'
    AND author NOT IN ('strands-agent', 'dependabot')
    AND repo IN ('agent-builder','agent-sop','docs','evals','mcp-server','private-docs-staging','private-sdk-python-staging','private-sdk-typescript-staging','private-tools-staging','samples','sdk-python','sdk-typescript','strands-action','strandsagents.com','tools','.github','private-samples-staging','private-strands-action-staging')
  GROUP BY author
),
daily_contributors AS (
  SELECT 
    date(created_at) as pr_date,
    author
  FROM pull_requests
  WHERE json_extract(data, '$.author_association') NOT IN ('OWNER', 'MEMBER', 'COLLABORATOR')
    AND author NOT LIKE '%[bot]%'
    AND author NOT IN ('strands-agent', 'dependabot')
    AND repo IN ('agent-builder','agent-sop','docs','evals','mcp-server','private-docs-staging','private-sdk-python-staging','private-sdk-typescript-staging','private-tools-staging','samples','sdk-python','sdk-typescript','strands-action','strandsagents.com','tools','.github','private-samples-staging','private-strands-action-staging')
  GROUP BY date(created_at), author
)
SELECT 
  CAST(strftime('%s', dc.pr_date) as INTEGER) as time,
  CASE WHEN fc.first_pr_date = dc.pr_date THEN 'New Contributors' ELSE 'Returning Contributors' END as metric,
  COUNT(DISTINCT dc.author) as value
FROM daily_contributors dc
JOIN first_contributions fc ON dc.author = fc.author
WHERE CAST(strftime('%s', dc.pr_date) as INTEGER) >= $__from / 1000
  AND CAST(strftime('%s', dc.pr_date) as INTEGER) <= $__to / 1000
GROUP BY dc.pr_date, metric
ORDER BY dc.pr_date ASC

panels.title: New vs Returning Contributors

panels.description: Follows date range. Percentage of contributors from 30-60 days ago who returned in last 30 days.

targets.queryText:
WITH date_series AS (
  SELECT DISTINCT date FROM daily_metrics
  WHERE CAST(strftime('%s', date) as INTEGER) >= $__from / 1000
    AND CAST(strftime('%s', date) as INTEGER) <= $__to / 1000
),
contributor_activity AS (
  SELECT DISTINCT
    date(created_at) as pr_date,
    author
  FROM pull_requests
  WHERE json_extract(data, '$.author_association') NOT IN ('OWNER', 'MEMBER', 'COLLABORATOR')
    AND author NOT LIKE '%[bot]%'
    AND author NOT IN ('strands-agent', 'dependabot')
    AND repo IN ('agent-builder','agent-sop','docs','evals','mcp-server','private-docs-staging','private-sdk-python-staging','private-sdk-typescript-staging','private-tools-staging','samples','sdk-python','sdk-typescript','strands-action','strandsagents.com','tools','.github','private-samples-staging','private-strands-action-staging')
),
prior_period AS (
  SELECT 
    ds.date as ref_date,
    ca.author
  FROM date_series ds
  JOIN contributor_activity ca 
    ON ca.pr_date > date(ds.date, '-60 days') 
    AND ca.pr_date <= date(ds.date, '-30 days')
  GROUP BY ds.date, ca.author
),
current_period AS (
  SELECT 
    ds.date as ref_date,
    ca.author
  FROM date_series ds
  JOIN contributor_activity ca 
    ON ca.pr_date > date(ds.date, '-30 days') 
    AND ca.pr_date <= ds.date
  GROUP BY ds.date, ca.author
),
retention_calc AS (
  SELECT 
    pp.ref_date,
    COUNT(DISTINCT pp.author) as prior_contributors,
    COUNT(DISTINCT CASE WHEN cp.author IS NOT NULL THEN pp.author END) as retained
  FROM prior_period pp
  LEFT JOIN current_period cp ON pp.ref_date = cp.ref_date AND pp.author = cp.author
  GROUP BY pp.ref_date
)
SELECT 
  CAST(strftime('%s', ref_date) as INTEGER) as time,
  'Retention Rate' as metric,
  CASE 
    WHEN prior_contributors = 0 THEN 0 
    ELSE ROUND(100.0 * retained / prior_contributors, 1) 
  END as value
FROM retention_calc
ORDER BY ref_date

  AND author NOT IN ('strands-agent', 'dependabot')
  AND repo IN ('agent-builder','agent-sop','docs','evals','mcp-server','private-docs-staging','private-sdk-python-staging','private-sdk-typescript-staging','private-tools-staging','samples','sdk-python','sdk-typescript','strands-action','strandsagents.com','tools','.github','private-samples-staging','private-strands-action-staging')
  AND CAST(strftime('%s', date(created_at)) as INTEGER) >= $__from / 1000
  AND CAST(strftime('%s', date(created_at)) as INTEGER) <= $__to / 1000
GROUP BY repo
ORDER BY unique_contributors DESC
targets.rawQueryText:

  COUNT(DISTINCT author) as unique_contributors
FROM pull_requests

  AND CAST(strftime('%s', date(created_at)) as INTEGER) <= $__to / 1000
GROUP BY repo
ORDER BY unique_contributors DESC

panels.description: Follows date range. Running total of first-time community contributors over time.

targets.queryText:
WITH first_contributions AS (
  SELECT 
    author,
    MIN(date(created_at)) as first_pr_date
  FROM pull_requests
  WHERE json_extract(data, '$.author_association') NOT IN ('OWNER', 'MEMBER', 'COLLABORATOR')
    AND author NOT LIKE '%[bot]%'
    AND author NOT IN ('strands-agent', 'dependabot')
    AND repo IN ('agent-builder','agent-sop','docs','evals','mcp-server','private-docs-staging','private-sdk-python-staging','private-sdk-typescript-staging','private-tools-staging','samples','sdk-python','sdk-typescript','strands-action','strandsagents.com','tools','.github','private-samples-staging','private-strands-action-staging')
  GROUP BY author
),
daily_new AS (
  SELECT 
    first_pr_date as date,
    COUNT(*) as new_contributors
  FROM first_contributions
  GROUP BY first_pr_date
)
SELECT 
  CAST(strftime('%s', d.date) as INTEGER) as time,
  'Cumulative Contributors' as metric,
  (SELECT SUM(new_contributors) FROM daily_new dn WHERE dn.date <= d.date) as value
FROM daily_metrics d
WHERE CAST(strftime('%s', d.date) as INTEGER) >= $__from / 1000
  AND CAST(strftime('%s', d.date) as INTEGER) <= $__to / 1000
GROUP BY d.date
ORDER BY d.date ASC
